short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: FreeSaver - Free save and share web contents

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Collect and share the best part of web page as you like.

FreeSaver can help you
-- download webpage
-- transfer parts of which you interested as online url and then send it to your email.

All of these can be done in just one click.
long.zh_CN,zh_TW:
收藏并分享任意页面内容

FreeSaver 是一个高效知识收集的 chrome 插件，可以帮助你：

-- 将当前页面 1: 1 完整样式地保存到本地
-- 只需一键，即可收藏任意你感兴趣的页面部分，将其存储为在线 url，并转发该链接到你的邮箱
